==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dandelion
<hw>Dan"de*li`on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>dent de
lion</ets> lion's tooth, fr. L. <ets>dens</ets> tooth + <ets>leo</ets>
lion. See <er>Tooth</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, and <er>Lion</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A well-known plant of the genus
<gen>Taraxacum</gen> (<spn>Taraxacum officinale</spn>, formerly called
<spn>Taraxacum Dens-leonis</spn> and <spn>Leontodos Taraxacum</spn>)
bearing large, yellow, compound flowers, and deeply notched
leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dander</ent>⟦br⟧
